reviews.text:
This is an awesome vape RdaJunkie, congratz! I'm mixing up big bottles of it. &#xD;
In the original I taste a drop of licorice from Inawera (Lukrecja), so I've added that at 0.25% to this mix and after a few days steep that little extra is there. (Might well be a flavourart licorice he uses though) &#xD;
But surely your recipe is the bomb as is.&#xD;
Let me know if you've tried it ok? Many thx ;)
